Mobiles.Name: keeper
Mobiles.Long_Description: The Keeper of the Elysium stands here, presiding over the gathering.
Mobiles.Description: The keeper of the Elysium must have been apointed by a powerful prince.

Mobiles.Name: retainer
Mobiles.Long_Description: The Retainer is looking for his master.
Mobiles.Description: This man is in the service of a powerful Vampire.

Mobiles.Name: gangrel ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Gangrel ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This rugged looking ghoul mirrors the lack
of concern for fashion that the Gangrel
typically have.

Mobiles.Name: tremere ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Tremere ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This eccentric looking ghoul is wearing a
charm given to him by his master.

Mobiles.Name: toreador ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Toreador ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This ghoul is strikingly beautiful, and was
most likely chosen for that reason by his
master.

Mobiles.Name: brujah ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Brujah ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This large ghoul is wearing heavy boots
and leather clothes.  Better watch him, he
looks like a trouble maker.

Mobiles.Name: malkavian ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Malkavian ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This ghoul looks like he's not all there.
For some reason he's wearing a dead chicken
on his head.

Mobiles.Name: cappadocian ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Cappadocian ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This poor ghoul looks like he was brought
back from the dead.  Half of the flesh on
his head is gone...

Mobiles.Name: nosferatu ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Nosferatu ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
My God! This horrifying creature is covered
with scales and pustulent sores.

Mobiles.Name: ventrue ghoul
Mobiles.Long_Description: A Ventrue ghoul stares at you vacantly.
Mobiles.Description:
This ghoul is well dressed and looks like
he was once an important and noble man.

Mobiles.Name: fido dog pet
Mobiles.Long_Description: A pet fido sniffs your feet.
Mobiles.Description:
This dog seems to know that something is
not quiet right.

Rooms.Name: The Entrance to the Elysium
Rooms.Description:
You stand before the entrance to the 
Elysium.  This place is set aside to show
all that enter about the world they have 
entered, and to prepare them for the
dangers they shall meet.

Rooms.Name: A junction in the hallways
Rooms.Description:
The Halls split here, be careful as you 
proceed.  Learn what you may, but know
that only a small amount of knowledge is
contained within.  To fully understand the
clans, you will have to research long
and hard.

Rooms.Name: The Halls of the Elysium
Rooms.Description:
The walls of this hall are made of ancient
stones and covered with arcane symbols
and great works of art.

Rooms.Name: The Skylight
Rooms.Description:
>From this high perch, you can see out into
a dark land, full of danger and intrigue.
If you dare venture out, watch yourself,
because the Vampires of this world follow
their traditions closely.  Make sure you
never anger one.

Rooms.Name: a Toreador Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Toreador has left a marker here
for all to see.  This clan is comprised
of artists, musicians, and writers.  The
clan of the rose is famous for its passion
for all things artistic.

Rooms.Name: a Ventrue Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Ventrue has left a marker here 
for all to see.  This clan is comprised
of leaders and politicians.  The Ventrue
are known for their impeccable taste and
tradition. They are masters of manipulation.

Rooms.Name: a Nosferatu Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Nosferatu has left a marker here
for all to see.  These vampires are hideosly
disfigured, and therefore have taken great
pains to perfect their ability to go unseen.
They are also known as information brokers.

Rooms.Name: a Gangrel Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Gangrel has left a marker here
for all to see.  The clan is comprised of
nomads and wanderers.  The Gangrel are fierce
warriors with close ties to the animal
world.

Rooms.Name: a Cappadocian Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Cappadocian has left a marker here
for all to see.  This clan is comprised
of necromancers and death prophets. These
vampires have made great strides towards
unlocking the secrets of death.

Rooms.Name: a Tremere Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Tremere has left a marker here 
for all to see.  This mysterious clan is
made up of a group of warlocks and magicians.
The Tremere are a clan with many rituals
and traditions.

Rooms.Name: a Malkavian Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Malkavian has left a marker here
for all to see. Every member of this clan is insane in some way. These vampires are
known for their madness, which they consider
a gift rather than a curse.

Rooms.Name: a Brujah Marker
Rooms.Description:
The clan Brujah has left a marker here
for all to see. This clan is comprised of
rebels and anarchs.  The Brujah are known for
their quick tempers and great fighting
abilities.
